text: Aattinakkare is a 1989 Indian Malayalam film, directed by SL Puram Anand, starring Sukumaran and Lissy Priyadarsan in the lead roles. ==Cast== * Lissy Priyadarsan * Sukumaran * Lalu Alex * Soorya ==References== ==External links== * Category:1989 films Category:Indian films Category:1980s Malayalam-language films
